<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ ài wǒ de ài wǒ yǐ jīng kàn jiàn, xīn zhōng bù zhù de tiào dòng,
 píng jìng de xīn zhōng yǒu le lián yī, kāi shǐ le xīn de háng chéng.
 bù zài qiú shì shàng de shén me, zhǔ zhè lǐ duō fēng fù,
 shēng mìng de yuán quán, huó shuǐ de jiāng hé, cì gěi xún qiú zhǔ de rén.
 a wǒ de xīn zài gē chàng, gē chàng zhè wèi yé sū!
 a wǒ de líng zài gē chàng, chēng xiè wàn wáng zhī wáng!</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ ài wǒ de ài 迦南38</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>38</hymn_number>
</song>